94\u201312301|pmc=3412024|date=2012-07-31}} \n* {{cite journal|last=Webb|first=Patrick|title=Support for agriculture during economic transformation|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|doi=10.1073/pnas.0913334108|pmid=21173245|volume=109|issue=31|pages=12309\u201312314|pmc=3411984|date=2012-07-31}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Maxwell|first=Daniel|title=Fit for Purpose|journal=Food Policy|doi=10.1016/j.foodpol.2009.10.002|volume=35|issue=2|pages=91\u201397|date=April 2010}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Webb|first=Patrick|title=Medium-to-long run implications of high food prices|url=http://jn.nutrition.org/content/140/1/143S.abstract|journal=Journal of Nutrition|volume=140|issue=1|pages=143S\u2013147S|accessdate=15 September 2011|doi=10.3945/jn.109.110536|pmid=19923389|year=2010}}\n\n'''Select Op-Eds/Interviews'''\n*[https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2015/oct/16/malnutrition-food-systems-consumption-better-data?CMP=share_btn_tw \"To end malnutrition we must step up to the plate with data on what people eat\"], theguardian, 16 October 2015.\n*[http://jiom.com.np/index.php?journal=jiomjournal&page=issue&op=view&path&#91;&#93;=60/ \"The Prize and the Price of Good Nutrition\"], Journal of the Institute of Medicine, December 2013.\n*[http://aboutharvest.com/2012/02/dr-patrick-webb-addressing-world-hunger/ \"Feeding 9 Billion\"], About Harvest, 14 February 2012. \n*[http://www.cbc.ca/thecurrent/episode/2011/07/25/somali-famine-crisis/ \"Somali Famine Crisis\"], [[Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]], 25 July 2011.\n*[http://www.wfp.org/aid-professionals/podcast/how-far-have-we-come-nutrition \"How far have we come on nutrition?\"], [[World Food Programme]], 17 June 2011.\n*[http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,,15051434,00.html \"Reducing Poverty Stresses Food Systems\"], ''[[Deutsche Welle]]'', 11 May 2011.\n*[http://www.voanews.com/english/news/usa/US-Looks-to-Supply-Healthier-Food-to-Worlds-Hungry---120781594.html \"US to Supply Healthier Food to Worl